<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmation d'inscription — {{ evenement.titre }}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box; }
        body { background:#f4f5fb;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;color:#1a1d2e; }
        .wrapper { max-width:600px;margin:32px auto;background:#fff;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 32px rgba(108,99,255,.1); }

        /* Header */
        .header { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6C63FF 0%,#9D6BFF 100%);padding:40px 40px 32px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden; }
        .header::before { content:'';position:absolute;top:-60px;right:-60px;width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08); }
        .header::after  { content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-40px;left:-40px;width:140px;height:140px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
        .header-logo { font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-bottom:16px; }
        .header-icon { width:64px;height:64px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:18px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:28px;margin-bottom:16px; }
        .header-title { font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;line-height:1.3; }
        .header-sub { font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);margin-top:8px; }

        /* Body */
        .body { padding:36px 40px; }

        /* Greeting */
        .greeting { font-size:16px;color:#4b5563;margin-bottom:24px;line-height:1.6; }
        .greeting strong { color:#1a1d2e; }

        /* Event card */
        .event-card { background:#f8f7ff;border:1.5px solid #ede9ff;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:28px; }
        .event-img { width:100%;height:160px;object-fit:cover;display:block; }
        .event-img-placeholder { width:100%;height:100px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6C63FF,#9D6BFF);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:36px; }
        .event-info { padding:20px 22px; }
        .event-title { font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1d2e;margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.3; }

        /* Details grid */
        .details-grid { display:table;width:100%;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0 8px; }
        .detail-row { display:table-row; }
        .detail-icon { display:table-cell;width:32px;vertical-align:middle;padding:4px 10px 4px 0; }
        .detail-icon span { display:inline-block;width:28px;height:28px;background:#ede9ff;border-radius:8px;text-align:center;line-height:28px;font-size:13px; }
        .detail-label { display:table-cell;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9ca3af;vertical-align:middle;padding-right:10px;white-space:nowrap; }
        .detail-value { display:table-cell;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1d2e;vertical-align:middle; }

        /* Status badge */
        .status-row { display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:#f0fdf4;border:1.5px solid #86efac;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:28px; }
        .status-label { font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#15803d; }
        .status-badge { background:#16a34a;color:#fff;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px; }
        .status-row.paid { background:#eff6ff;border-color:#93c5fd; }
        .status-row.paid .status-label { color:#1d4ed8; }
        .status-row.paid .status-badge { background:#2563eb; }

        /* Info box */
        .info-box { background:#faf9ff;border-left:4px solid #6C63FF;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:28px;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.7; }

        /* CTA */
        .cta { text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px; }
        .cta-btn { display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6C63FF,#9D6BFF);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:.02em; }

        /* Footer */
        .footer { background:#f8f7ff;border-top:1px solid #ede9ff;padding:24px 40px;text-align:center; }
        .footer-text { font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.8; }
        .footer-brand { font-weight:700;color:#6C63FF; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">

    {# ── Header ── #}
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-logo">PathFinder RH</div>
        <div class="header-icon">🎉</div>
        <div class="header-title">Inscription confirmée !</div>
        <div class="header-sub">Votre place est réservée pour cet événement</div>
    </div>

    {# ── Body ── #}
    <div class="body">

        <p class="greeting">
            Bonjour <strong>{{ prenom }} {{ nom }}</strong>,<br>
            Votre inscription à l'événement suivant a bien été enregistrée.
        </p>

        {# Event card #}
        <div class="event-card">
            {% if evenement.imagePath %}
                <img src="{{ app.request.schemeAndHttpHost }}/{{ evenement.imagePath }}" alt="{{ evenement.titre }}" class="event-img">
            {% else %}
                <div class="event-img-placeholder">📅</div>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="event-info">
                <div class="event-title">{{ evenement.titre }}</div>
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <div class="detail-icon"><span>📅</span></div>
                        <div class="detail-label">Début</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{ evenement.dateDebut|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <div class="detail-icon"><span>🏁</span></div>
                        <div class="detail-label">Fin</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{ evenement.dateFin|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                    </div>
                    {% if evenement.lieu %}
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <div class="detail-icon"><span>📍</span></div>
                        <div class="detail-label">Lieu</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{ evenement.lieu }}</div>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if evenement.categorie %}
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <div class="detail-icon"><span>🏷️</span></div>
                        <div class="detail-label">Catégorie</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{ evenement.categorie.nomCategorie }}</div>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <div class="detail-icon"><span>👥</span></div>
                        <div class="detail-label">Type</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{ evenement.typeEvenement }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# Payment status #}
        {% if statutPaiement == 'PAYE' %}
        <div class="status-row paid">
            <span class="status-label">💳 Paiement reçu</span>
            <span class="status-badge">Payé</span>
        </div>
        {% elseif statutPaiement == 'NON_REQUIS' %}
        <div class="status-row">
            <span class="status-label">✅ Événement gratuit</span>
            <span class="status-badge">Gratuit</span>
        </div>
        {% else %}
        <div class="status-row">
            <span class="status-label">⏳ Paiement en attente</span>
            <span class="status-badge" style="background:#d97706">En attente</span>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        {# Ticket ref #}
        <div style="background:#f0eeff;border:1.5px solid #ddd6fe;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;">
            <div>
                <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9ca3af;margin-bottom:3px;">Référence du ticket</div>
                <div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#6C63FF;letter-spacing:.06em;">{{ ticketRef }}</div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:28px;">🎟️</div>
        </div>

        {# Info box #}
        <div class="info-box">
            Votre ticket PDF est joint à cet email. Présentez-le à l'entrée de l'événement.
            Conservez également cet email comme preuve d'inscription.
        </div>

        {# CTA #}
        <div class="cta">
            <a href="{{ eventUrl }}" class="cta-btn">Voir l'événement →</a>
        </div>

    </div>

    {# ── Footer ── #}
    <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
            Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement par <span class="footer-brand">PathFinder RH</span>.<br>
            Ne pas répondre à cet email. Pour toute question, connectez-vous à votre espace personnel.<br>
            <span style="font-size:11px;color:#c4c9d4">© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} PathFinder — Tous droits réservés</span>
        </p>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
